name: My Mind Wandered 11"x11" print
description:
High-quality giclée reproduction print from an original artwork by Becky Joye. Printed on archival, acid-free, 100% cotton Epson fine art paper.

11"x11" image size, with 1/2" white border for framing. (Fits 12"x12" frame)

Limited edition print from set of 50.
Signed, dated, and numbered on the back of print.

Ships in cardboard shipping tube within 3-5 days of order via USPS Priority Mail. Shipping is a flat-rate of $6.00. At this time, I am only shipping within the United States.

Sales tax rate of 6.75% applies to North Carolina residents.

©2012 Becky Joye
